00:24:54,168 --> 00:24:56,432
In the bathroom. Shaved it off.

355
00:24:56,604 --> 00:24:58,366
Well, how come?

356
00:24:59,706 --> 00:25:01,764
Because banks don't like beards.

357
00:25:01,941 --> 00:25:03,498
So we called ourselves Apple...

358
00:25:03,675 --> 00:25:05,835
...and started making
those little computers.

359
00:25:06,010 --> 00:25:08,069
Me, Steve and his friends
Elizabeth and Dan.

