Oh, right. I'm sorry. Mike Markula.

367
00:25:28,358 --> 00:25:30,518
- Hey, Mike. How you doing?
- I'm well.

368
00:25:30,693 --> 00:25:32,717
The man who put intelligence
into Intel.

369
00:25:32,894 --> 00:25:34,122
- Yeah...
- No smoking in here.

370
00:25:34,296 --> 00:25:36,559
Oh, I'm sorry about that. Yeah.

371
00:25:36,730 --> 00:25:38,697
- Valentine said you might call.
- Yeah.

372
00:25:38,865 --> 00:25:41,765
- Welcome to Apple Computers.
