437
00:29:43,494 --> 00:29:45,358
Well, I don't know.

438
00:29:45,528 --> 00:29:47,461
I don't know.

439
00:29:57,403 --> 00:29:58,961
Okay.

440
00:29:59,404 --> 00:30:01,338
- Two thousand.
- Four thousand.

441
00:30:01,639 --> 00:30:03,572
- What?
- Of course.

442
00:30:03,841 --> 00:30:06,274
Next, Ed, this business
of a $ 15 royalty...

443
00:30:06,442 --> 00:30:09,968
