457
00:31:01,578 --> 00:31:04,342
Chris, you've been here two days,
and you're into blackjack?

458
00:31:04,515 --> 00:31:06,209
Yeah, so?

459
00:31:06,382 --> 00:31:08,212
So you got work to do.

460
00:31:12,987 --> 00:31:14,647
Oh, God, no.

461
00:31:14,821 --> 00:31:17,311
Not Frank Sinatra. Not "My Way. "

462
00:31:17,489 --> 00:31:19,422
Not again. Spare us.

